,1146,1147],"warning",{},[245,1148,1149,1150,1155,1156,1160,1161,1164],{},"本文发表于 ",[248,1151,1154],{"href":1152,"rel":1153},"https://github.com/nuxt/content",[252],"Content"," 和 ",[248,1157,253],{"href":1158,"rel":1159},"https://github.com/nuxtlabs/studio-module",[252]," 模块于 2025 年 1 月 6 日合并之前。因此，文中内容可能存在一些不一致之处。Studio 模块现已废弃，并作为 Content 模块的可选功能提供。请参阅 ",[248,1162,1163],{"href":6},"此指南"," 了解如何启用。",[277,1166,1168,1155,1170,1172],{"id":1167},"yaml-和-json-文件的自动生成表单",[256,1169,54],{},[256,1171,58],{}," 文件的自动生成表单",[271,1174],{":controls":273,":loop":273,"src":1175},"https://res.cloudinary.com/nuxt/video/upload/v1730132248/yml-json-form_n9czcs.mp4",[245,1177,1178,1179,1155,1181,1183],{},"延续我们让 Nuxt Studio 成为非技术用户编辑 Nuxt 网站内容工具的旅程，我们很高兴地宣布，现在可以通过生成的视觉表单来编辑 ",[256,1180,54],{},[256,1182,58],{}," 文件。这次更新免去了用户直接操作复杂文件语法（如 YAML 或 JSON）的需求。",[1185,1186,1188],"callout",{"icon":1187},"i-ph-info",[245,1189,1190],{},"目前数组尚未通过表单支持，但我们计划在 Nuxt Content v3 发布集合和用户定义的 schema 后进行支持。详见下文章节。",[303,1192,1193],{"id":1193},"同步导航",[245,1195,1196,1197,1200],{},"此次更新同时改进了非 Markdown 格式（如 YAML 和 JSON）预览与所选文件间的同步导航。请将 Studio 模块更新至最新版本 ",[256,1198,1199],{},"v2.2.0"," 以应用此修复。",[277,1202,1204],{"id":1203},"迈向-nuxt-content-v3","迈向 Nuxt Content v3",[245,1206,1207,1208,1215],{},"我们很高兴地宣布，Nuxt Content v3 的第四个 alpha 版本已发布，且 ",[248,1209,1212],{"href":1210,"rel":1211},"https://content.nuxt.com/",[252],[281,1213,1214],{},"草稿文档"," 已开放。",[303,1217,1219],{"id":1218},"下一步","下一步？",[245,1221,1222],{},"未来几个月，我们将专注于测试和优化 Nuxt Content v3，确保其稳健且适合生产环境发布。以下是与 Nuxt Studio 相关的主要改进：",[976,1224,1225,1239,1253],{},[979,1226,1227,1230,1231,1234,1235,1238],{},[281,1228,1229],{},"合并 Studio 模块","：不久后，Studio 模块将直接集成进 Nuxt Content。Nuxt Content v3 发布后，只需在 ",[256,1232,1233],{},"nuxt.config.ts"," 文件中设置 ",[256,1236,1237],{},"content.editor: true"," 即可启用 Studio。该简化意味着无需额外模块，安装更快捷。",[979,1240,1241,1244,1245,1155,1249,1252],{},[281,1242,1243],{},"统一文档","：模块合并后，我们将把 ",[248,1246,1154],{"href":1247,"rel":1248},"https://content.nuxt.com",[252],[248,1250,253],{"href":250,"rel":1251},[252]," 的文档及网站合并为一个综合资源。Studio 平台本身（用户登录后可用）将作为独立站点保留。",[979,1254,1255,1258,1259,1261],{},[281,1256,1257],{},"充分利用 Studio 中的数据结构和集合","：借助 Nuxt Content v3，Studio 平台将支持并适配 ",[248,1260,25],{"href":32}," 和用户定义的 schema，实现针对 YAML、JSON 文件及 Markdown 的 front-matter 的基于 schema 的表单生成。",[245,1263,1264],{},"这些更新体现了我们为您的 Nuxt 网站提供最佳内容编辑平台的承诺。敬请期待！",{"title":345,"searchDepth":374,"depth":374,"links":1266},[1267,1271],{"id":1167,"depth":374,"text":1268,"children":1269},"YAML 和 JSON 文件的自动生成表单",[1270],{"id":1193,"depth":387,"text":1193},{"id":1203,"depth":374,"text":1204,"children":1272},[1273],{"id":1218,"depth":387,"text":1219},"studio","2024-10-28T01:00:00.000Z","通过自动生成的表单编辑 YAML 和 JSON 文件。",{"src":1278},"/docs/studio/json-yml-forms.png",{"name":1138},"/changelog/yaml-json-form",{"title":1138,"description":1276},"changelog/yaml-json-form","Nber8GtPQz-10nHLhPkV1dBjV9zGSaqnxyunR6gJTZQ",{"id":1285,"title":1286,"authors":1287,"body":1290,"category":1274,"date":1857,"description":1858,"draft":42,"extension":1127,"image":1859,"meta":1861,"navigation":226,"path":1862,"seo":1863,"stem":1864,"__hash__":1865},"posts/changelog/frontmatter-form.md","可视化 Front-matter 编辑",[1288],{"name":237,"avatar":1289,"to":238},{"src":240},{"type":242,"value":1291,"toc":1846},[1292,1308,1312,1318,1322,1326,1334,1339,1342,1345,1348,1352,1360,1364,1376,1379,1382,1390,1393,1397,1400,1404,1410,1414,1417,1706,1710,1713,1716,1837,1843],[1145,1293,1294],{},[245,1295,1296,1297,1155,1300,1303,1304,1307],{},"本文发布于 2025 年 1 月 6 日 ",[248,1298,1154],{"href":1152,"rel":1299},[252],[248,1301,253],{"href":1158,"rel":1302},[252]," 模块合并之前。因此，本文可能存在一些不一致之处。Studio 模块现已弃用，作为 Content 模块的可选功能提供。请参阅",[248,1305,1306],{"href":6},"这份指南","了解如何启用。",[277,1309,1311],{"id":1310},"可视化-front-matter-编辑","可视化 Front-Matter 编辑",[245,1313,1314,1315,1317],{},"现在您无需编写 ",[256,1316,54],{}," 语法即可编辑 markdown front-matter。Nuxt Studio 会自动生成用户友好的表单，简化元数据编辑。",[271,1319],{":autoplay":273,":controls":273,":loop":273,"poster":1320,"src":1321},"https://res.cloudinary.com/nuxt/video/upload/v1729157955/frontmatterform2_rmh58v.jpg","https://res.cloudinary.com/nuxt/video/upload/v1729157955/frontmatterform2_rmh58v.mp4",[277,1323,1325],{"id":1324},"什么是-front-matter","什么是 Front-matter？",[245,1327,1328,1329,1333],{},"Front-matter 是基于 Markdown 的 CMS 中用于为页面提供元数据（如描述、标题等）的约定。在 ",[248,1330,1332],{"href":1331},"/docs/files/markdown#front-matter","Nuxt Content"," 中，front-matter 使用的是 YAML 语法。",[1185,1335,1336],{"icon":1187,"to":1331},[245,1337,1338],{},"关于 front-matter 语法的详细信息，请参阅 Nuxt Content 文档。",[277,1340,1341],{"id":1341},"我们非技术编辑器的最后一环",[245,1343,1344],{},"Nuxt Studio 从发布编辑器起就以非技术用户为设计核心。我们的目标是让每个人都能轻松编辑 markdown 和内容。",[245,1346,1347],{},"自动生成 front-matter 表单是下一步的合理进展。通过摆脱 YAML 语法的复杂性，简化了非开发者的编辑流程，提供动态输入选项，如图片选择器、日期选择器、布尔切换等。此增强使我们实现了完全可视化且用户友好的内容管理体验。",[277,1349,1351],{"id":1350},"扩展至所有-yaml-和-json-文件","扩展至所有 YAML 和 JSON 文件",[245,1353,1354,1355,1155,1357,1359],{},"不久之后，表单生成功能将扩展至您在 Nuxt Studio 中编辑的所有 ",[256,1356,54],{},[256,1358,58],{}," 文件，让结构化数据的操作更为轻松便捷。",[277,1361,1363],{"id":1362},"展望-nuxt-content-v3","展望 Nuxt Content v3",[1185,1365,1367],{"icon":1366},"i-ph-lightbulb",[245,1368,1369,1370,1375],{},"本节内容仅为 ",[248,1371,1374],{"href":1372,"rel":1373},"https://github.com/nuxt/content/tree/v3",[252],"Nuxt Content v3"," 的预告，我们将很快发布更详尽的博文。",[245,1377,1378],{},"我们正积极开发下一重大版本 Nuxt Content，这将带来显著的性能提升和新功能，进一步提升内容管理体验。",[303,1380,1381],{"id":1381},"性能优化",[245,1383,1384,1385,1389],{},"Nuxt Content v2 的一大挑战是需要较大的包体积来存储所有内容文件，这在向边缘平台（如 ",[248,1386,124],{"href":1387,"rel":1388},"https://hub.nuxt.com/",[252],"）部署时造成了问题。",[245,1391,1392],{},"为解决此问题，Nuxt Content v3 在生产环境中不再使用基于文件的存储方式，而是采用 SQL 数据库系统。此变更对用户透明。我们为开发模式、静态生成、服务器渲染及通过 NuxtHub 的边缘部署提供零配置支持。",[303,1394,1396],{"id":1395},"引入-collections集合","引入 Collections（集合）",[245,1398,1399],{},"Collections 是 Nuxt Content 项目中相关内容项的分组，帮助更高效地组织和管理大型数据集。",[1038,1401,1403],{"id":1402},"定义-collections","定义 Collections",[245,1405,1406,1407,1409],{},"您可以在 ",[256,1408,343],{}," 文件中定义 collections，Nuxt Content 将用它配置数据库结构、类型工具及用于查找、解析和查询内容的方法。",[1038,1411,1413],{"id":1412},"collections-方案schema","Collections 方案（Schema）",[245,1415,1416],{},"方案可确保 collections 内部的一致性，并改善 TypeScript 类型定义，增强与 Nuxt Content 工具的集成。",[339,1418,1420],{"className":341,"code":1419,"filename":343,"language":344,"meta":345,"style":345},"import { defineCollection, z } from '@nuxt/content'\n\n// 导出 collections\nexport const collections = {\n  // 使用 `defineCollection` 工具定义 collection\n  posts: defineCollection({\n    // 指定该 collection 中内容的类型\n    type: 'page',\n    // 加载匹配此模式的所有文件\n    source: 'blog/**/*.md',\n    // 为该 collection 定义自定义 schema\n    schema: z.object({\n      date: z.date(),\n      image: z.object({\n        src: z.string(),\n        alt: z.string()\n      }),\n      badge: z.object({\n        label: z.string(),\n        color: z.string()\n      })\n    })\n  }),\n}\n",[256,1421,1422,1448,1453,1459,1475,1480,1493,1498,1513,1518,1534,1539,1556,1573,1590,1607,1623,1631,1648,1665,1680,1686,1692,1701],{"__ignoreMap":345},[349,1423,1424,1427,1430,1432,1434,1436,1438,1441,1443,1445],{"class":351,"line":352},[349,1425,1426],{"class":355},"import",[349,1428,1429],{"class":370}," {",[349,1431,395],{"class":366},[349,1433,520],{"class":370},[349,1435,448],{"class":366},[349,1437,627],{"class":370},[349,1439,1440],{"class":355}," from",[349,1442,410],{"class":370},[349,1444,324],{"class":413},[349,1446,1447],{"class":370},"'\n",[349,1449,1450],{"class":351,"line":374},[349,1451,1452],{"emptyLinePlaceholder":226},"\n",[349,1454,1455],{"class":351,"line":387},[349,1456,1458],{"class":1457},"sHwdD","// 导出 collections\n",[349,1460,1461,1463,1467,1470,1473],{"class":351,"line":402},[349,1462,356],{"class":355},[349,1464,1466],{"class":1465},"spNyl"," const",[349,1468,1469],{"class":366}," collections ",[349,1471,1472],{"class":370},"=",[349,1474,384],{"class":370},[349,1476,1477],{"class":351,"line":423},[349,1478,1479],{"class":1457},"  // 使用 `defineCollection` 工具定义 collection\n",[349,1481,1482,1485,1487,1489,1491],{"class":351,"line":440},[349,1483,1484],{"class":377},"  posts",[349,1486,381],{"class":370},[349,1488,395],{"class":362},[349,1490,367],{"class":366},[349,1492,371],{"class":370},[349,1494,1495],{"class":351,"line":461},[349,1496,1497],{"class":1457},"    // 指定该 collection 中内容的类型\n",[349,1499,1500,1503,1505,1507,1509,1511],{"class":351,"line":495},[349,1501,1502],{"class":377},"    type",[349,1504,381],{"class":370},[349,1506,410],{"class":370},[349,1508,414],{"class":413},[349,1510,417],{"class":370},[349,1512,420],{"class":370},[349,1514,1515],{"class":351,"line":551},[349,1516,1517],{"class":1457},"    // 加载匹配此模式的所有文件\n",[349,1519,1520,1523,1525,1527,1530,1532],{"class":351,"line":570},[349,1521,1522],{"class":377},"    source",[349,1524,381],{"class":370},[349,1526,410],{"class":370},[349,1528,1529],{"class":413},"blog/**/*.md",[349,1531,417],{"class":370},[349,1533,420],{"class":370},[349,1535,1536],{"class":351,"line":588},[349,1537,1538],{"class":1457},"    // 为该 collection 定义自定义 schema\n",[349,1540,1541,1544,1546,1548,1550,1552,1554],{"class":351,"line":634},[349,1542,1543],{"class":377},"    schema",[349,1545,381],{"class":370},[349,1547,448],{"class":366},[349,1549,451],{"class":370},[349,1551,454],{"class":362},[349,1553,367],{"class":366},[349,1555,371],{"class":370},[349,1557,1558,1561,1563,1565,1567,1569,1571],{"class":351,"line":652},[349,1559,1560],{"class":377},"      date",[349,1562,381],{"class":370},[349,1564,448],{"class":366},[349,1566,451],{"class":370},[349,1568,563],{"class":362},[349,1570,476],{"class":366},[349,1572,420],{"class":370},[349,1574,1575,1578,1580,1582,1584,1586,1588],{"class":351,"line":662},[349,1576,1577],{"class":377},"      image",[349,1579,381],{"class":370},[349,1581,448],{"class":366},[349,1583,451],{"class":370},[349,1585,454],{"class":362},[349,1587,367],{"class":366},[349,1589,371],{"class":370},[349,1591,1592,1595,1597,1599,1601,1603,1605],{"class":351,"line":700